---
title: Chicken Breast Chasseur Style Pasta with Mushrooms and Cheese
description: This Chicken Breast Chasseur Style Pasta is a crowd pleaser and is one to get the family round the dinner table for. Super simple to make, and easily customised to suit the kids too.
